                        </decoDesc>
                        <additions>
                            <p>Some corrections, additions and extra verses have been added in the
                                margins. </p>
                            <p>A table of contents on f. 1r lists the 7 <term>fātiḥas</term> and
                                their folio numbers. </p>
                            <p>An undated note on f. 1r mentions that <persName role="fmo" key=""
